   <item>
      <title>Blackleaf Gloves</title>
      <category>Common</category>
      <fluff>Made from the leaves of an ancient Feywild oak, these well-preserved black gloves increase the utility of your pact boon</fluff>
      <level>
         <value>4</value>
         <price>840</price>
      </level>
      <level>
         <value>14</value>
         <price>21,000</price>
      </level>
      <level>
         <value>24</value>
         <price>525,000</price>
      </level>
      <type>Hands Slot</type>
      <block>
         <name>Utility Power</name>
         <keyword>Teleportation</keyword>
         <frequency>Encounter</frequency>
         <action>Free</action> <subaction>Reaction</subaction>
         <line><name>Trigger</name>Your Pact Boon triggers</line>
         <line><name>Effect</name>You teleport 2 squares.</line>
         <line indent="1"><name>Level 14</name>Teleport 3 squares.</line>
         <line indent="1"><name>Level 24</name>Teleport 4 squares.</line>
         <line>If you have the <![CDATA[<i>misty step</i>]]> Pact Boon power, you instead either increase the maximum distance of that teleportation, or teleport an ally that was adjacent to the creature that triggered your Pact Boon.</line>
      </block>
   </item>
   
